ghtman\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"injury woes\", \"from\": 217, \"to\": 228}, {\"ngram\": \"his Olympic lifeline\", \"from\": 272, \"to\": 292}, {\"ngram\": \"Paris\", \"from\": 296, \"to\": 301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The 30-year-old thought his dream of a second Olympic appearance was over when a muscle tear in his calf ruled him out ofthe UK Athletics Championships last month.\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 473, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 435, \"end\": 461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"UK Athletics Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q623109\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UK_Athletics_Championships\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his dream\", \"from\": 334, \"to\": 343}, {\"ngram\": \"a second Olympic appearance\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 374}, {\"ngram\": \"a muscle tear\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 402}, {\"ngram\": \"his calf\", \"from\": 406, \"to\": 414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after selection rival Elliot Giles tripped up in the closing stages of the 800m, Wightman received a discretionary pick for Team GB and is now determined to make the most of the reprieve.\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 666, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 501, \"end\": 513, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elliot_Giles\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Elliot Giles\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elliot_Giles\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Elliot_Giles\"}, {\"begin\": 603, \"end\": 610, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9962660556862435, \"rank\": 0.003531017838328299, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the closing stages\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 546}, {\"ngram\": \"the 800m\", \"from\": 550, \"to\": 558}, {\"ngram\": \"Wightman\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 568}, {\"ngram\": \"a discretionary pick\", \"from\": 578, \"to\": 598}, {\"ngram\": \"the reprieve\", \"from\": 653, \"to\": 665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's been a big relief to know that I can still go to the Olympic Games and try and achieve what I wanted to,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 668, \"to\": 788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big relief\", \"from\": 679, \"to\": 691}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Games\", \"from\": 723, \"to\": 740}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am pretty grateful that I got the nod for that.\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 840, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the nod\", \"from\": 823, \"to\": 830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I tried not to think about the alternative, because it would be a bit crushing.\", \"from\": 841, \"to\": 920, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the alternative\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sadly, it's meant that others have had to have that feeling, which is not very nice, especially when they are people you get on with.\", \"from\": 921, \"to\": 1054, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"that feeling\", \"from\": 968, \"to\": 980}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 1031, \"to\": 1037}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stay in the game with The Turnover: your weekly roundup of sport business news, expert analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories from City AM's sports desk.\", \"from\": 1056, \"to\": 1209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the game\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1072}, {\"ngram\": \"The Turnover\", \"from\": 1078, \"to\": 1090}, {\"ngram\": \"your weekly roundup\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1111}, {\"ngram\": \"sport business news\", \"from\": 1115, \"to\": 1134}, {\"ngram\": \"analysis and behind\\u2011the\\u2011scenes stories\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1181}, {\"ngram\": \"City AM's sports desk\", \"from\": 1187, \"to\": 1208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But the only way you can make sure you feel better is if you go out and perform as well as you can and do it justice, which is what I know I need to do.\", \"from\": 1211, \"to\": 1364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the only way\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1228}, {\"ngram\": \"justice\", \"from\": 1321, \"to\": 1328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They have given me the chance to compete because they feel I am the right person to do that, so I have got to prove them right.\\\"\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1493, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1394}, {\"ngram\": \"the right person\", \"from\": 1429, \"to\": 1445}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wightman is one 1,100 elite athletes funded by the National Lottery on the World Class Programme, which allows them to train full time, have access to the world's best coaches and benefit from pioneering technology, science, and medical support.\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1740, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wightman\", \"from\": 1495, \"to\": 1503}, {\"ngram\": \"one 1,100 elite athletes\", \"from\": 1507, \"to\": 1531}, {\"ngram\": \"the National Lottery\", \"from\": 1542, \"to\": 1562}, {\"ngram\": \"the World Class Programme\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1591}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1642}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's best coaches\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1670}, {\"ngram\": \"technology\", \"from\": 1699, \"to\": 1709}, {\"ngram\": \"science\", \"from\": 1711, \"to\": 1718}, {\"ngram\": \"medical support\", \"from\": 1724, \"to\": 1739}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A world champion over 1500m in 2022in a race his father Geoff famously called from the commentary box, Wightman is now readying himself for battle over two laps.\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1903, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"1500m\", \"from\": 1764, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"a race\", \"from\": 1780, \"to\": 1786}, {\"ngram\": \"his father\", \"from\": 1787, \"to\": 1797}, {\"ngram\": \"Geoff\", \"from\": 1798, \"to\": 1803}, {\"ngram\": \"the commentary box\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1843}, {\"ngram\": \"Wightman\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1853}, {\"ngram\": \"battle\", \"from\": 1882, \"to\": 1888}, {\"ngram\": \"two laps\", \"from\": 1894, \"to\": 1902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I do not believe that I have ever wanted to just go to the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1974, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 1973}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's about going there and being able to try and come back with something, which is what I still want to try and do, even if it's not the event I originally thought I was going to,\\\" he added.\", \"from\": 1975, \"to\": 2166, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2048}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 2109, \"to\": 2118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You look at the legacies of Seb Coe, Steve Cram, Steve Ovett and Kelly Holmes, who were able to run over 800m and 1500m, and I do not see why that has to change.\", \"from\": 2168, \"to\": 2330, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2197, \"end\": 2204, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seb Coe\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sebastian_Coe\"}, {\"begin\": 2212, \"end\": 2223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Cram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cram, Steve\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Cram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Cram\"}, {\"begin\": 2212, \"end\": 2223, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Cram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Cram, Steve\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Cram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Cram\"}, {\"begin\": 2224, \"end\": 2229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Ovett\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7325349380545307e-45, \"text\": \"Ovett\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Ovett\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Steve_Ovett\"}, {\"begin\": 2234, \"end\": 2246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelly Holmes\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Holmes\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the legacies\", \"from\": 2181, \"to\": 2193}, {\"ngram\": \"800m\", \"from\": 2274, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"1500m\", \"from\": 2283, \"to\": 2288}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I can win Olympic gold over 800m, that's almost a better CV than having won two in 1500m - 800m Olympic champion and 1500m world champion is a pretty good career.\", \"from\": 2332, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2393, \"end\": 2395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Curriculum_vitae\", \"score\": 0.9999930965365823, \"rank\": 6.717196427357935e-06, \"text\": \"CV\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Curriculum_vitae\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Curriculum_vitae\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic gold\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2358}, {\"ngram\": \"800m\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2368}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic champion\", \"from\": 2432, \"to\": 2448}, {\"ngram\": \"1500m\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2458}, {\"ngram\": \"world champion\", \"from\": 2459, \"to\": 2473}, {\"ngram\": \"a pretty good career\", \"from\": 2477, \"to\": 2497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am looking at all the positives that can come from this and it's a chance to showcase that I can run over both distances pretty well.\\\"\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2635, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the positives\", \"from\": 2515, \"to\": 2532}, {\"ngram\": \"a chance\", \"from\": 2566, \"to\": 2574}, {\"ngram\": \"both distances\", \"from\": 2607, \"to\": 2621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wightman has had his path to Paris followed by Channel 4 cameras and is one of a number of Team GB stars to be involved in new fly-on-the-wall documentary Path to Paris: The Hunt for Gold, supported by The National Lottery.\", \"from\": 2637, \"to\": 2860, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2666, \"end\": 2671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999963040409, \"rank\": 3.695919020212473e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2684, \"end\": 2693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Channel_4\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.871667597290001e-13, \"text\": \"Channel 4\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Channel_4\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Channel_4\"}, {\"begin\": 2728, \"end\": 2735, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9962660556862435, \"rank\": 0.003531017838328299, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 2800, \"end\": 2805, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999963040409, \"rank\": 3.695919020212473e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2839, \"end\": 2859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_L